name: Treedia Labs
overview: Treedia Labs develops feed-based media technology, brands, and communities. It offers media aggregation and distribution platforms that provide feed management and distribution to various Internet connected devices. The company’s products include Treedia feed management platform, which supports various forms of RSS-based feeds. The company serves cell phones, mp3/mp4 devices, Internet radio devices, Web browsers, video game devices, and IPTV/cable set-top devices markets. Treedia Labs was founded in 2006 and is based in Cambridge, Massachusetts.
